Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:04.34,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Keep the room well-lit and watch from a distance, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:05.22,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:36.57,On Screen red,CAPTION,0,0,0,,[Gintoki was swallowed up by the alien that grew to a humongous size.]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:42.28,On Screen red,CAPTION,0,0,0,,[What is it that Umibozu saw as he searched for Kagura?]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:47.74,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)神楽～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:49.29,On Screen,CAPTION,0,0,0,,["You Know What Happens if You Pee on a Worm"]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)神楽！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.52,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:53.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい しっかりしろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:53.13,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Hey! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙って見てたのか…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:02.41,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,You bastards... Did you just sit there and watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:03.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)ﾃﾒｴら\N黙って見てたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:07.43,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,After my daughter saved your lives... as she grew weaker and weaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:07.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)助けてもらっておいて\Nｵﾚの娘が弱っていくのを…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙って見てたのかって\N聞いてんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:10.27,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Did you just sit there and watch her die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:13.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾀ皇子)ままま 待て！\Nだって こんな状況じゃ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:15.01,Main01,PRINCE HATA,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait! In this situation, we couldn't call a doctor, even if we tried... Right, Jii?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,医者 呼ぶにも…｡ なぁ じい？\N(じい)ﾜｼに ふるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:17.22,Main01,JII,0,0,0,,Don't pass it to me! I don't know what happened! I don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らん！ ﾜｼは知らん！\N今日から ﾎﾞｹたから！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.12,Main01,,0,0,0,,I'm still in shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.28,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾃﾒｴ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)ﾊﾟﾋﾟｰ ﾀﾞﾒよ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:27.96,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Pappy, don't. Not after I saved their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく 私 助けたのに…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)神楽！\Nもう 大丈夫だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.08,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Kagura! It's okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.46,Main01,,0,0,0,,Daddy's going to take care of you! You don't have to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんが助けてやるから\Nもう 安心しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.15,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,I've changed, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:35.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 変わったでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:39.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の力\N人を傷つけるだけじゃないよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:42.47,Main01,,0,0,0,,My strength is not just for hurting people. I can protect people too, now, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:42.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人を守ることも\Nできるようになったよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:44.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう いい｡ しゃべるな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.77,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Don't talk anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:48.37,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,When I did...I made so many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:48.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)そういうふうにしたらね\Nいっぱい 友達できたよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)もう 独りじゃないね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.87,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,I'm not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:55.42,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,The Yato fought, and fought, and destroyed themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)戦って 戦って\N夜兎 滅びたね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:59.78,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,The Yato fought, and fought, and found themselves all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:59.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦って 戦って\N夜兎 独りぼっちになったね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.36,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Pappy, big brother...everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾊﾟﾋﾟｰも兄ちゃんも みんな…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:09.33,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,The ones we have to fight are ourselves. If we don't...everyone will be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:06.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦わなきゃいけないのは\N自分自身ｱﾙ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:09.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ みんな\N独りぼっちになってしまうよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:16.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(えいりあんの うなり声)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)ぐっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！\Nぐはっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:24.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾊﾟﾋﾟｰ… うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:26.85,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Pappy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:32.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神楽！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.51,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神楽～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.36,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:39.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《銀ちゃん…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.90,Main01,KAGURA (M),0,0,0,,Gin...chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:42.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,銀ちゃん…》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.23,Main01,KAGURA (M),0,0,0,,Gin-cha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(銀時)でぇいっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神楽～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.06,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《銀ちゃん…》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.23,Main01,KAGURA (M),0,0,0,,Gin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:03.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:05.76,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Damn earthworm monster! Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この みみず野郎！ ｿｲﾂを離せ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｼｮﾝﾍﾞﾝ かけんぞ！\N甘～いｼｮﾝﾍﾞﾝ かけんぞ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:09.13,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Or I'll...I'll piss on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:13.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)そんなことしたらなぁ\N大事なところが 腫れあがるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.76,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.73,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Your you-know-what will swell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.31,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Didn't your mother...ever teach you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,母ちゃんに習わなかったか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:20.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よぅ 今さら\N何をしにきた？ 若造｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:20.59,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Aren't you a bit late to be showing up now, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どのﾂﾗさげて\Nここに来れたんだ ﾃﾒｴは｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.97,Main01,,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,祭りが大好きでね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:28.60,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I love spectacles. Don't you? Fires, fights and aliens are what Edo is famous for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火事とｹﾝｶと えいりあんは\N江戸の華ってな｡ 知らねえかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)知るか！\Nえいりあん以上に 不快な野郎だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.33,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,All I know is...you're a pain in the ass!! Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:33.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失せやがれ！\Nうるせえ！ お前 腕が折れてるぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.88,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Shut up! At least I still have two arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,病院 行け!!\Nお前が行け！ 風邪ひけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.85,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,My one arm is worth three of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:38.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は 風邪をこじらせろ！\Nお前が こじらせろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:41.30,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?! Well, three of mine are worth six of yours!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:41.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校を ２～３日 休んで\N休みあけに ﾁﾔﾎﾔされろぃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(じい/ﾊﾀ)うわぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:45.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:49.83,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,You should go home! Go to a hospital and get a new brain to go with your new arm!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから お前は 早く帰れって｡\N病院 行って 早く➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕に ﾏｲﾅｽﾄﾞﾗｲﾊﾞｰつけてこい！\N(星海坊主)誰が つけるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:54.61,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,If I get a new brain, it'll be to bring one back for you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾏｲﾅｽなんて\Nあんまり使わねえじゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:54.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちかっつうと ﾌﾟﾗｽがいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:59.45,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,And I'm not going to a hospital for just an arm! My left arm was a prosthetic anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:57.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)だいたい\N腕の１本や２本で 病院なんざ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もともと義手なんだよ\Nｵﾚの左腕は！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:02.09,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Have them make you a prosthetic head while they're at it, you barcode-headed geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついでに 頭も作ってもらえ\Nすだれじじい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:06.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(えいりあんの うなり声)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(爆発音)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:12.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)止めろ！ なんとしても\Nここで くい止めるんだ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:12.66,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,Stop it! Your reign of terror ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:15.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)ﾔﾂらを\N江戸の街にいれるな～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.16,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,Don't let them get into the streets of Edo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:19.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊士)副長！ ﾀｰﾐﾅﾙの設備が\Nもう ﾒﾁｬｸﾁｬなんですが！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:19.23,Main01,MEMBER B,0,0,0,,Vice-chief! The terminal is coming apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.23,Main01,,0,0,0,,They're not going to blame us, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊士)これ\N責任問題になりませんか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:24.95,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,Who cares? We'll just say that the monster destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:25.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(土方)知るか｡ 全部\Nあのﾊﾞｹﾓﾉが壊したことにするぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:31.54,Main01,KETSUNO ANNOUNCER,0,0,0,,Viewers, did you hear that? Despite specific orders from the government, the Shinsen-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(結野ｱﾅ)ﾃﾚﾋﾞの前の皆さん\N聞きましたでしょうか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:31.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々は 今 目の前で\N不正が起こる瞬間を…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾒﾗﾏﾝ)ぐはぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:42.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁっ あれを見ろ！\Nえいりあんが ひいてくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:39.68,Main01,MEMBER F,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.09,Main01,MEMBER G,0,0,0,,The alien is retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったぁ ｵﾚたちの勝ちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.87,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,We did it! We've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 違う｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.52,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,No, we haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:49.53,Main01,MEMBER D,0,0,0,,Wh-What's it doing?! The alien is wrapping around the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊士)なんだ ありゃ！\Nえいりあんが 船に集まってくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:53.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が起こっているのでしょうか？\Nあそこに いったい何が… あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:53.53,Main01,KETSUNO ANNOUNCER,0,0,0,,What's happening? What is going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.14,Main01,MEMBER D,0,0,0,,Look! There's someone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊士)見ろ 誰かいるぞ！\N(隊士)えいりあんの中心！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.03,Main01,MEMBER F,0,0,0,,Right in the middle of the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:00.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊士)えいりあんの中心で\N何か叫んでる！ 何か叫んでるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:06:00.07,Main01,MEMBER G,0,0,0,,Amid a maelstrom of jaws, someone is yelling! They're shouting something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(土方)星海坊主!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.70,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,Umibozu? That's...Umibozu! And that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:04.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(土方)ありゃ 星海坊主だ！\Nそれに 野郎も！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:07.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どけ！\N(星海坊主)小便 かけんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.81,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.14,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Or we're gonna piss on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:12.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが 星海坊主…\Nまるで ﾊﾞｹﾓﾉじゃねえか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.97,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,That's Umibozu? He's like a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(沖田)いやいや\N旦那も負けてませんぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.32,Main01,OKITA,0,0,0,,No, no... Boss is keeping up with his pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:19.31,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,With them there, we can't just carelessly shoot. They'll be caught in the crossfire...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:18.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし あれじゃ\Nこちらも うかつに手が出せん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:20.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾔﾂらまで巻き込… ん!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(土方)あれは… 幕府の軍艦｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:23.06,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,Those are...Bakufu warships.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:26.12,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,It's Pops! Old man Matsudaira is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:26.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)とっつぁんだ！\N松平の とっつぁんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)破壊神 松平 片栗虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:29.26,Main01,OKITA,0,0,0,,The god of destruction! Katakuriko Matsudaira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)やばいって…\Nあのおっさんが通ったあとは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:32.84,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,We've got trouble! After that old guy is done, only ashes will be left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾁﾘも残らねえぞ！\Nﾀｰﾐﾅﾙも消しかねねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.45,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,He'll take out the entire terminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だぁ～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:39.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たぁっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おうおう…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:43.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)今頃 うるせえのが\Nﾌﾞﾝﾌﾞﾝ たかってきたぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.81,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Looks like they've finally shown up for their photo op!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:46.39,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,We've just about taken care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう ほとんど\Nｶﾀついたんじゃねえのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:49.16,Main01,,0,0,0,,I've got to hand it to you, punk, for an Earthling, you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…にしても ﾃﾒｴ\N地球人にしちゃ やるな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾃﾒｴに言われても\N嬉しくねえよ ﾊﾞｹﾓﾝめ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.86,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,That means a whole lot of nothing coming from you, monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,片腕で よく ここまで\N暴れられたもんだぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:55.26,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you fought this far with just one arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)ﾃﾒｴも 片腕じゃねえか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.03,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,You only have one arm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:59.18,Main01,,0,0,0,,For your own sake, go home. You'll die if you stay any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いことは言わねえ 帰れ｡\N死ぬぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:03.53,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I'd love to, but I don't see any exits around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰りてえけど\Nどっから帰りゃいいんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,非常口も見当たらねえよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.48,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I can't figure you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:07.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾃﾒｴの腹が読めねえ｡\N神楽を突き放しておきながら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:09.67,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,You pushed Kagura away, so what are you doing here? Why do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで ここにいる？\Nなんで ここまでやる？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:14.55,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I'd like to know the same thing. Why did I come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚが聞きてえくらいだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで こんなところに\N来ちまったかなぁ ｵﾚは｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.96,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前…｡\N安心しな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:20.23,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Relax. I'm not planning on taking that loudmouth brat back with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:20.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな うるせえｶﾞｷ\N連れ戻そうなんて腹はねえ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:22.55,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,And of course, I'm not planning on dying either. It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん 死ぬつもりもねえ｡\Nだが…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:26.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｱｲﾂを死なせるつもりもねえよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.29,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let her die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾊﾊﾊ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:31.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)おもしれえ…\Nおもしれえよ お前｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.57,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Interesting. You're an interesting fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.30,Main01,,0,0,0,,I think I understand why Kagura likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)神楽が気に入るのも\Nわかった気がする｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.87,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,But what can you do with only one arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 腕１本で 何ができるよ？\Nｱﾝﾀも１本だろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.40,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,You only have one arm, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.81,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)いやいや…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(銀時/星海坊主)\N合わせりゃ ２本だ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.47,Main01,GINTOKI/UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Together, we've got two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:50.60,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,It makes me sick to do it, but I'll help you until we rescue Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:50.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,胸ｸｿ悪いが 神楽 助けるまでは\N協力してやるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがたく思え 父さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.28,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Count your blessings, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:55.04,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I see... Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:55.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかい！ ｿｲﾂは ありがとよ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:58.96,Main01,OKITA,0,0,0,,What's that? The ship's keel, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:00.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ？ 船の底が…｡\Nおい ありゃ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.56,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,H-Hey, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.63,Main01,MEMBER F,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊士)な… なんだ ありゃ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:09.13,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,The nucleus. The core of the parasitic alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,核だ…｡ 寄生型えいりあんの中枢｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)こんな でけえのは\N初めて見るが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.75,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,It's the first one I've seen that's this huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾀｰﾐﾅﾙのｴﾈﾙｷﾞｰを 過度に吸収し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:16.31,Main02,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,It's absorbed an excessive amount of the terminal's energy and finally blew right through the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,肥大化し\N船底を破っちまったようだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:20.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれをつぶせば\Nｺｲﾂらを止められ… はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:19.38,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,If we smash that, we'll be able to stop this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.66,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,か… 神楽!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.91,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.84,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,It swallowed her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 飲まれちまったぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やばい…｡ このままじゃ\Nｺｲﾂを仕留めることはできねえ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:39.33,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,We've got a problem... We can't kill it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)ｺｲﾂをやれば\N神楽も死ぬ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.72,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,If we do, Kagura will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.57,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)聞け～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:49.06,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,All civilians in the terminal vicinity! Leave the area immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)ﾀｰﾐﾅﾙ周辺に留まっている\N民間人に告ぐ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:49.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)ただちに\Nﾀｰﾐﾅﾙから離れなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:54.11,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,We are about to open fire on the alien! Vacate the area immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)今から えいりあんに\N一斉放射を仕掛ける！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:54.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)ただちに 離れなさい！\Nなんだと!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.23,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.11,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:58.48,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,Pops, wait! A civilian child has been sucked into the alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:56.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっつぁん 待て！\N民間人のｶﾞｷが １人➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えいりあんに取り込まれている！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:03.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)近藤… ｶﾞｷ１人の命と江戸を\N同じ秤に かけるつもりか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:03.28,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Kondo... Are you weighing the life of a single civilian with all of Edo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人を救うってことはな➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:07.73,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Our mission is to save as many lives as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人を殺める以上の度胸が\N必要なんでぃ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:11.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大儀を見失えば\N救える命も 救えなくなるぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:12.96,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Would you risk your entire mission for just one of those lives? Don't be a wussy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,甘ったれてんじゃねえよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:15.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし とっつぁん！\N局長！ えいりあんが！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.44,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,But, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.97,Main01,MEMBER D,0,0,0,,Chief, the alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:18.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)ｸｿｯ\Nまた 動き出しやがった！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.04,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,Damn! It's on the move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:21.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほ～ら みろ｡ おじさんの\N言うことを聞かないから｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.95,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,You see what I mean? That's what happens when you don't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な？ おじさんの言うことは\Nだいたい正しいんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:28.05,Main01,,0,0,0,,But Pops knows best, doesn't he? I'm made up of 80 percent correctness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:28.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おじさんの80ﾊﾟｰｾﾝﾄは\N正しさで できていま～す｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:32.90,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,You two go on home! You're in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)そういうことだからさぁ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らも 家に帰りんさい｡\Nｼﾞｬﾏだ｡ ﾍﾟｯ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行け…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.24,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.85,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,This place will soon be a sea of flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)\Nもうじき ここは 火の海だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.86,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,You...aren't thinking of doing this alone, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:39.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾃﾒｴ まさか １人で…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)つくづく\N情けねえ男だよ ｵﾚは｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:48.45,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I'm a real loser. I'm called the fiercest there is, but I can't protect anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:46.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最強だ なんだと\N言われたところでよ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何にも守れやしねえ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:52.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家族ひとつ…\N娘 １人 守れやしねえんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.80,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Not my family... Not my only daughter... Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.77,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,The Yato fought, and fought, and found themselves all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((神楽:戦って 戦って\N夜兎 独りぼっちになったね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:10:00.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦わなきゃならないのは\N自分自身ｱﾙ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:03.21,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,The ones we have to fight are ourselves. If we don't...everyone will be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ みんな\N独りぼっちになってしまうよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これも 逃げ続けてきた代償か｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.37,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,This the price I have to pay for running away for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:08.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまねえ 神楽…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.52,Main01,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kagura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せめて 最期は\Nお前と一緒に死なせてくれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.28,Main01,,0,0,0,,At least let me die together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:18.83,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,This is why daughters get mad at their fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:19.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだからよぉ 世の中の親父は\N娘に煙たがられちまうのかねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:24.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おとうさんよ ｱﾝﾀ ﾃﾒｴのｶﾞｷ １人\N信じることができねえのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:25.33,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Look dad, can't you even trust your own kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:28.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｱｲﾂが こんなもんで死ぬﾀﾏだと\N思ってんのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:28.24,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Do you think she's so weak that a little thing like this'll kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:32.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５分だ｡\N５分だけ 時間を稼いでくれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:31.79,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Five minutes. Just delay 'em five minutes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:35.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚを信じろとは言わねえ｡ だが！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:35.21,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to believe in me. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:38.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｱｲﾂのことは信じてやってくれよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.82,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,At least believe in Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 なにを…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.51,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,What're you planning to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:45.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《な… なんてﾏﾈしやがるんだ》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:47.87,Main01,UMIBOZU (M),0,0,0,,What a crazy thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:52.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(砲撃音)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうすんだ？ 近藤さん｡\N(近藤)ｸｯ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:10:59.29,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do, Kondo-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:03.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)松っちゃん砲 発射用意！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:03.17,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Ready the Matsu-Blaster for firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.17,Main01,SUBORDINATE A,0,0,0,,Commissioner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:05.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(部下)長官！\N(松平)いいから撃て｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:05.35,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Never mind. Just fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(部下)いや\Nそうじゃなくて あれを…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.15,Main01,SUBORDINATE B,0,0,0,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:08.40,Main01,SUBORDINATE B,0,0,0,,Look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:11.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(部下)ﾔﾂら\N逃げるどころか増えてます｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.44,Main01,SUBORDINATE A,0,0,0,,They didn't leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.68,Main01,SUBORDINATE A,0,0,0,,In fact, there are more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:12.88,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.76,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,You dumb-asses! Can't you see this old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(新八)ｷｻﾏら！ このおっさんが\N目に入らねえか!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 撃ったら もれなく\Nこのﾊﾞｶ皇子も爆死するぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.72,Main01,JII,0,0,0,,If you shoot now, this idiot prince will be blasted to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もれなく国際問題だぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.88,Main01,JII,0,0,0,,You'll have an international incident on your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:23.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(じい)５分でいいから\N待てって言ってんだよ ｺﾗ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.56,Main01,JII,0,0,0,,Just wait five minutes, that's all we ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.99,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,Sure, what difference could five minutes make?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５分なんて すぐじゃん！\N矢のごとしじゃん!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｶｯﾌﾟうどんでも作って\N待ってろって言ってんだよ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.63,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,Go make yourself some instant ramen while you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾃ… ﾃﾒｴら…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:30.63,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Y-You people...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:33.55,Main01,JII,0,0,0,,That girl saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの娘には世話になったんでな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:36.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,撃たないよね？ これ｡\N大丈夫だよね～？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:36.41,Main01,PRINCE HATA,0,0,0,,They won't shoot, will they? We'll be all right, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:38.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく あの天然ﾊﾟｰﾏが！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:41.59,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,That darn wavy head! If he was intent on coming, he should've said so at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来るなら来るって\N最初から言えってんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ来ると思ってたけどね…\Nあまのじゃくが｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:45.98,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,Well, I knew he was going to come, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:49.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((神楽:私 変わったでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:49.78,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,I've changed, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:55.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)私 人を守ることも\Nできるようになったよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:55.26,Main01,,0,0,0,,I can protect people too, now, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:12:00.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)そういうふうにしたらね\Nいっぱい友達できたよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:12:00.54,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,When I did...I made so many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:03.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)もう 一人じゃないね))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.15,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,I'm not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.35,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Kagura...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:06.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神楽！ 起きろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.51,Main01,,0,0,0,,Wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぎ… 銀ちゃん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.11,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Gi...Gin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:15.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほ～ら 酢昆布 食べちゃうぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:15.64,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Look, I'm gonna eat all your pickled seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:23.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(部下)長官！ あれ 本物です!!\N本物のﾊﾀ皇子です！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:23.65,Main01,SUBORDINATE A,0,0,0,,Commissioner... He's the real thing! The real Prince Hata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして あんなところに…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.55,Main01,SUBORDINATE A,0,0,0,,What's he doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おぅ これか…｡\N松っちゃん砲のｽｲｯﾁ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.38,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Oh, is this it? Is this the Matsu-blaster firing button?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:32.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(部下)いや そうですけど…｡\N早く救助しないと大変なことに｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:31.66,Main01,SUBORDINATE B,0,0,0,,Uh...yeah... But we have to quickly rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:35.77,Main01,SUBORDINATE B,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you just push that? You're kidding! You just pushed it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(部下)あれ？ 今 押した？\Nｳｿ！ 今 押した!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやぁ ５時から\N娘のﾊﾟｰﾃｨｰあるからして…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:39.04,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,I have to be at my daughter's birthday party at five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:41.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(部下)えぇ～っ 止めろ～！\N(部下)もうﾑﾘだ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:41.32,Main01,SUBORDINATE A,0,0,0,,What?! We have to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.41,Main01,SUBORDINATE B,0,0,0,,It can't be stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(じい)あれ？\Nなんか撃とうとしてない？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:44.23,Main01,JII,0,0,0,,Does it look like they're starting to fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾀ)ｳｿだろ？ 仮にも皇子だよ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.32,Main01,PRINCE HATA,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right? I am a prince, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やばいって これ！\N早く逃げないと…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.11,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,We're in trouble. We gotta get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:51.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)ｳｶﾞ～ｯ！\Nそれ 私の酢昆布ね!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:52.13,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,That's my pickled seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:54.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)うりゃあ～！\N(星海坊主)神楽!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.80,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！\Nお前…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:56.92,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,You did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:01.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく 食い意地が張ったｶﾞｷだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:01.22,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Man, that kid sure gets vicious about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親の顔が見てみてえな！ おい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.23,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Did her parents starve her or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)ｵﾚも見てみてえよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:07.64,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,You know what I wonder? Did your parents cut out your brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のような\Nﾑﾁｬｸﾁｬな男の親の顔を…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:11.68,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Maybe I never had any parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:11.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男は 下の毛が生えたら もう\Nﾃﾒｴでﾃﾒｴを 育てていくもんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)ｸｸｯ… 違いねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.27,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,That I can believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:17.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さぁて そろそろ…｡\Nしまいにしようか！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.27,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Now then, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.14,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Let's finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:20.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくぜ！ おとうさん!!\N誰が おとうさんだ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.11,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Let's do it, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.74,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Who're you calling "dad"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:26.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊士たち)あぁっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.95,Main01,MEMBER D,0,0,0,,Look! The alien is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊士)見ろ！ えいりあんが!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:31.46,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,Pops! Stop the attack! There's no need to shoot anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:31.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっつぁん！ 砲撃を止めろ!!\Nもう撃つ必要はねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,泊める？ ふざけるな！\N栗子は まだ17歳だぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.32,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Stop? Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.25,Main01,,0,0,0,,Kuriko is still seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼氏と２人で\N誕生日を祝いたいとは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.51,Main01,,0,0,0,,She said she wants to celebrate her party alone with her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぬかしてやがったが…\Nあれ 外泊する気だよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:41.43,Main01,,0,0,0,,But she plans on staying out all night. I absolutely won't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:42.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対 許さねえ！\N全力で ｼﾞｬﾏしてやる!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:46.00,Main01,,0,0,0,,I'll do everything I can to stop it. I'll even dance the Lambada on top of her cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:45.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｹｰｷの上で 思いきり\Nﾗﾝﾊﾞﾀﾞ 踊ってやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢泊める｣じゃなくて ｢止める｣！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:49.97,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,Not stop as in "stop over"! Can't you think of anything else except your daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｱﾝﾀ 娘のことしか\N考えてねえのか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:53.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)うるせえな！ どうせもう\N今さら中止できねえんだろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.45,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Quiet! I can't stop it now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)早く逃げろ～！\Nおっさん 知らないからな!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:58.62,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get out of there! I won't be responsible for whatever happens to you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)おっさんは\N一切 責任とりません！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ!? 逃げろったって\Nどこ逃げろっていうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:01.06,Main01,JII,0,0,0,,Huh? Run? Where are we supposed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾒｶﾞﾈ… ﾒｶﾞﾈ… ﾒｶﾞﾈ…｡\N下は ﾑﾘだ！ 上だ 上!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:01.85,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,My glasses... My glasses... My glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.90,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Down's no good. Go up. Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:06.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,酢昆布 返せ～！\Nうぉ～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.76,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Give me back my pickled seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:12.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神楽！ しっかりしろ!!\Nおい ﾀﾞﾒだって！ 出血が…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.25,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Kagura, pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.63,Main01,,0,0,0,,Stop it, he's bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《星海坊主:意識が定まってねえ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:17.29,Main01,UMIBOZU (M),0,0,0,,She's not fully conscious. She broke through the nucleus in this condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな状態で\N核を ぶち破ってきたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:21.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男の声が… 神楽の意識の\N底にまで届いたってのか？》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.77,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,This man's voice reached into the depths of Kagura's subconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:23.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ 酢昆布だ…｡\N(星海坊主)えっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.64,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Ah! Pickled seaweed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(じい/新八)うわっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:31.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｷﾞｬ～ 何すんの？\Nおとうさんの大事な昆布が…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:31.91,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! Pappy's precious hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！ 何 食ってんだ!!\N出せ！ ﾊｹﾞるぞ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.41,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:36.29,Main01,,0,0,0,,Spit it out! You'll go bald! You'll go bald if you eat that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもん食ったら ﾊｹﾞるぞ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ？ なに？ この音｡\N(砲撃音)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.66,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:43.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(着弾音)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:49.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(爆発音)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(部下)目標 消滅を確認｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.82,Main01,SUBORDINATE A,0,0,0,,Destruction...confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんてこった…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.67,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,My...god...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)まさか あの連中が…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.92,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,Those guys must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.28,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)傘一本で…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.50,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,With just an umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:29.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(松平)あの砲撃を…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:28.87,Main01,MATSUDAIRA,0,0,0,,he blocked the blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぼ… 坊主さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:31.17,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,B-Bozu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:33.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)\Nｵﾚも 焼きが まわったようだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:34.13,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Looks like I got a bit fired up myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 髪の毛も\N焼きが まわってるけど…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.77,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Your hair is on fire, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:41.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他人を守って くたばるなんざ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:39.91,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Imagine me dying...to save somebody else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.02,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.11,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,Bozu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坊主さん！\Nﾊｹﾞ！ おい ﾊｹﾞ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.46,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Baldy! Hey, Baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.77,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,Bal...I mean... Bozu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:48.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾊ… じゃない… 坊主さん！\Nﾊｹﾞ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.89,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Baldy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右側だけ ﾊｹﾞ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:52.95,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Baldy, but only on the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:16:02.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾍﾘｺﾌﾟﾀｰの飛行音)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:06.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾀ)いやぁ 一時は\Nどうなることかと思ったけどね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:06.14,Main01,PRINCE HATA,0,0,0,,At one point, I really thought it was the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:10.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,得意の空手で なんとか\N乗り切れたみたいな感じみたいな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:10.38,Main01,PRINCE HATA,0,0,0,,but I prevailed with my exceptional kara-tay skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:14.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(土方)おぅおぅ…\Nどうすんだ？ この死骸の山｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.11,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,What're we going to do with this mountain of dead alien flesh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(沖田)ﾀｰﾐﾅﾙも\Nしばらく運休らしいですぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:17.11,Main01,OKITA,0,0,0,,The terminal will be out of service for a while, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(土方)上に なに言われるか\Nわかったもんじゃねえよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:20.73,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,No telling what the higher-ups are going to say. That old man, for chrissake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:20.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく あのじじい…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.36,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,But that monster was every bit what the rumors said he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても\Nｳﾜｻどおりのﾊﾞｹﾓﾝだったな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:26.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？\N星海坊主だよ 星海坊主…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.28,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,I mean Umibozu... Umibozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚは 正直\Nえいりあんなんぞより➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:30.82,Main01,HIJIKATA,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I was way more scared of him than the alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのおっさんのほうが\Nよっぽど恐ろしかったね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:35.29,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,Really? He didn't look like a monster to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:36.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか？ ｵﾚには ﾔﾂが\Nﾊﾞｹﾓﾉになんて見えなかったけどな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:40.48,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,He just looked like any father, struggling to protect his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:40.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)娘を守ろうとｼﾞﾀﾊﾞﾀする\Nただの人の親に見えたよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:44.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)ｶﾞｷに手をやく\Nその辺にいる ただの親に…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.83,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,A father just like any other around here, having trouble with his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(近藤)捜し物とやらは\N見つかったのかね？ 星海坊主殿｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:49.13,Main01,KONDO,0,0,0,,Did you find what you were looking for, Umibozu-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 神楽は？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.46,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,How's Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)\N救護班に 手当てを受けてる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.96,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,She's being treated by the rescue team. Her injury was pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けっこうな深手だったんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:59.05,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you get treated, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｱﾝﾀも手当てしてもらったほうが\Nいいんじゃねえのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:02.22,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I told you, my left arm was a prosthetic from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから この左腕は\Nもとから義手だって言ってんだろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:05.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新調しなきゃな…｡\N腕じゃねえよ 頭だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.89,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I just need to get a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:05.45,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Not your arm...your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう意味だ？\Nそういう意味だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:06.79,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:08.11,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか ああいう意味か？\N殺すぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.71,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Oh, in that case, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:15.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｸｯ とうとう腕だけじゃなくて\N毛まで なくなっちゃったな…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:15.20,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Now, I'm missing not only my arm, but my hair, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:18.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのうち生えてくるさ｡\N腕が生えるかよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.97,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,It'll grow back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.49,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Arms don't grow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:20.28,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Not your arm... Your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕じゃねえよ 頭だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:26.72,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I see... My hair, eh? All you talk about is my hair. I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:22.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか 頭か…｡ あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 頭のことしか\Nしゃべってねえじゃねえか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:28.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺すぞ…｡ まっ でもな➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:31.83,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,But anyway, both of them serve as a lesson to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:31.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｺｲﾂは 両方 ｵﾚにとっちゃ\N戒めなのかもしれねえよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戒め？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.46,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,A lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.33,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I lost it to my own kid, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｺｲﾂは ﾃﾒｴのｶﾞｷにやられたのさ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:41.36,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Not Kagura. I have an older kid, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:41.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神楽じゃねえぞ…｡\N上に もう一人いてな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:45.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｺｲﾂが とんでもねえ性悪でよ…\Nいや 性悪というか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.94,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,That one's a real bad egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:48.54,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,No...not bad, let's just say he faithfully carried the blood of the Yato Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜兎の特性を\N忠実に受け継いだというか…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,闘争本能の塊のようなｶﾞｷでな…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:51.30,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,He's a kid who's the personification of the fighting spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)はるか昔 夜兎族には➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:57.37,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,A long time ago, the Yato clan had a terrible custom called "Parent Killing."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親殺しという\Nとんでもねえ風習があったのさ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:18:00.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親を超えてなんぼという\N野蛮な ならわしが…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:18:00.67,Main02,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,It was a savage practice where a person's worth was determined by surpassing their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつの頃か消えた\Nそんな いにしえの ならわしを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:07.10,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,These days, that practice has all but disappeared, but he tried to revive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:07.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,野郎は このご時世に\N実践しようとしやがったのさ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:10.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)天下の星海坊主のｸﾋﾞを\Nとろうとしやがった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:10.63,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,He tried to take the head of the legendary Umibozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:15.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,驚いたか？ だが 夜兎ってのは\Nそういう種族なんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:15.67,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Surprised? That's what we Yato are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:20.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのときにな\Nｵﾚも気づいちまったのさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:20.89,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,When it happened, I suddenly realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:23.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚのｸﾋﾞを狙うｶﾞｷを前にして\N止めるのではなく➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.21,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Squaring off with my own son, who was going for my neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:27.91,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,That I wasn't trying to stop him... I was trying to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:27.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気で息子を殺そうとしている\Nｵﾚの中の血によ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.07,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,If Kagura hadn't stopped me, I would have murdered him for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:34.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)神楽が止めなければ\N確実に殺してた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのときのｵﾚを見る\Nﾔﾂらの おびえた目は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:39.47,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Even now, I can't forget the fear I saw in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今でも忘れられねえ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:44.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことがあってから\Nｵﾚは 家に寄りつけなくなってな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:44.80,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,After that, I couldn't go near my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神楽も いつか ﾔﾂのように➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:48.74,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I was afraid that Kagura would one day seek my life as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚの命を\N狙ってくるんじゃねえかって…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:54.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとき ｵﾚは 自分のなかの獣を\N抑えることができるのかって…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:53.45,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I was overwhelmed with the fear, that if she did,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不安で しかたなくてな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.91,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I would not be able to suppress the beast inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:59.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変わる度胸も\N信じる度胸もなかった ｵﾚは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:59.33,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I didn't have the courage to change, or to trust myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:02.85,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,so I ran away, leaving young Kagura and her dying mother behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幼い神楽と 死にかけた母ちゃんを\N残して 逃げ回った｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:05.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家族を壊すのが怖かった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:08.73,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I was afraid of destroying my family, but in the end, not a trace of my family remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果 家族なんて\N跡形もなく消えちまったよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神楽に\Nｵﾚと同じ思いをさせまいと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:15.42,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I came all this way, because I didn't want Kagura to go through the same thing I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:15.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなところまで\Nｱｲﾂを追いかけてきちまった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.07,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,But I almost repeated the same mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:19.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚは また同じことを\N繰り返そうとしていたんだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)お前に言われて\Nﾊｯとなったよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.18,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,When you told me, it hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき ｵﾚを止めてくれたのも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:26.74,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,It was Kagura who stopped me then, and it was always Kagura who supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも ｵﾚを支えてくれたのも\N神楽だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな神楽を 何一つ\N信じちゃいなかったんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:30.97,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,That's how she is, and yet I couldn't even trust her one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分を見て\N神楽を見たつもりでいた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:38.62,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I thought I saw myself in Kagura. But Kagura and I are different. She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚと神楽は 違う｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:40.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｱｲﾂは… ｱｲﾂは ｵﾚなんかより➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:42.13,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,She's a lot stronger than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと 強いﾔﾂなんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:50.28,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,But I-I'm a total failure as a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)それを ｵﾚってﾔﾂは…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全に 父親失格だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:55.85,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,No...maybe I'm the only one who thinks I'm a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:53.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 親父と思ってるのは\Nｵﾚだけで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｱｲﾂは ｵﾚみたいなﾔﾂのこと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親父とさえ\N思ってねえのかもしれねえな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:58.11,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Maybe she doesn't even think of me as her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.51,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,A letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手紙｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんかいつも ｺｿｺｿ書いてたぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:05.03,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,She always wrote them in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:09.32,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Since you had no permanent address, they were always sent back to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｱﾝﾀ 住所不定みたいだから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも\Nうちに返されてきたけどな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡す機会があるかもって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:14.57,Main02,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I secretly kept all of them in my closet hoping if I ever got the chance to hand them to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,内緒で全部\N押し入れに取ってあるが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は これしかねえや｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.39,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,This is the only one I have right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:20.19,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Oh, and don't worry, I'd never do anything so crass as to read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっと 安心しな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中身を見るような\Nﾔﾎﾞなﾏﾈは してねえよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:24.05,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I figured you're not the type...to read this and go nuts about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:25.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついでにｱﾝﾀも これ見て\Nｸﾞﾀﾞｸﾞﾀﾞ言うほど ﾔﾎﾞじゃねえよな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:27.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあな！\Nおい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.60,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.75,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.34,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I don't know all the details, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:30.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,細けえことは よくわからねえや｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど\N自分を想ってくれる親がいて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:34.79,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,If you have a parent who cares about you, what more do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他に 何がいるよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.78,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I wish I had one... A family like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚは 欲しかったよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｱﾝﾀみてえな家族が｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:42.17,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:42.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.77,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Ironic, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皮肉なもんだな｡\Nﾎﾝﾄに大事なもんってのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:48.79,Main02,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,How the people who don't have things...usually understand them better than the ones who do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってるﾔﾂより\N持ってねえﾔﾂのほうが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:50.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知ってるもんさ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:54.27,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,So...cherish her... Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:52.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからよぉ ｱｲﾂのこと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大事にしてやってくれよな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:21:02.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言っとくけどね➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:08.82,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,Let me make this clear. I'm staying at the Odd Jobs for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ﾎﾞｸは ずっと\N万事屋にいますからね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:11.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家族と\N思ってくれていいですからね！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:10.93,Main01,SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,You can think of me as family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:15.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.46,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Didn't he say he was quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめるとか言ってなかったっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:21.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)ﾌﾌｯ ｢大事にしろ｣か…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.31,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Cherish her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:27.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(星海坊主)お～い\N聞いてるか 神楽｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.86,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you listening, Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:29.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうことだから お父さん➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:32.59,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,That's the deal. From now on... Daddy will cherish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから お前を\N大事にすることになったから｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:36.14,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,So be happy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:37.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 元気でやれよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.09,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Pappy! Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)ﾊﾟﾋﾟｰ 待って｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.28,Main01,,0,0,0,,Wait, Pappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待って ﾊﾟﾋﾟｰ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:44.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:48.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)｢拝啓 お父さん｡\Nしばらく会っていませんが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.66,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Dear Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:51.26,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you in a while. Are you well? I'm doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:51.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元気ですか？ 私は元気です｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は今\N侍という 不思議な連中が住む➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:57.62,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Right now, I am living in a city called Edo with some strange people called samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:58.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,江戸という街に住んでいます｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:00.80,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,They are truly strange creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らは\N本当に不思議な生き物です｡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:05.54,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,Even though they're usually all weak, hopeless and pathetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:05.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふだんは みんな 弱くて ｼｮﾎﾞくて\Nﾀﾞﾒ野郎ばかりなのに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いざというときは\N武士道という信念で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:13.58,Main02,KAGURA,0,0,0,,when it really counts, they call on some idea called "Bushido" and become these tough, noble warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:11.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分を たたき上げ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:14.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に折れない\N屈強な戦士になるのです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:17.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜兎も侍も みんな変わりません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:20.17,Main02,KAGURA,0,0,0,,And they have something in common with the Yato. They're all fighting against themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.47,0:22:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 自分と戦っています｡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:23.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでなら\N私は変われる気がします｡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:23.70,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,I think if I stay here I can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:27.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと 自分に負けない自分に\Nなれると思うのです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:27.62,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,I think I can become a person who doesn't give in to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:31.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうしたら お父さん\Nきっと 私を➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:33.70,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,If I do change, Pappy... I want you to take me with you on your travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:34.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒に\N旅に連れて行ってくださいね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:36.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お父さんと一緒に\N宇宙を まわって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:40.96,Main02,KAGURA,0,0,0,,My dream is to travel through the universe with you...and become the top alien hunter in the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:39.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宇宙一の えいりあんはんたーに\Nなるのが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:41.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の夢です｡ 神楽より｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:42.30,Main01,,0,0,0,,Love, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:48.54,Main01,UMIBOZU,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:48.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってるぞ 神楽｡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:54.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
